              "correctAnswer": "13",
              "explanation": "Maximum occurs when sets are disjoint: |A ∪ B| = |A| + |B| = 5 + 8 = 13",
              "difficulty": 1,
              "points": 2,
              "timeLimitSeconds": 45
            }
          ]
